and in USD I think we're up to about 2 million total in revenue and we have 5-ish full-time

25
00:01:02,053 --> 00:01:02,373
staff.

26
00:01:02,513 --> 00:01:05,835
Everything's a little bit ish in the indie world, but that's kind of where we are.

