take care of some marketing and PR, a little bit of design,

30
00:01:17,581 --> 00:01:19,283
a bunch of other stuff at Clever Endeavor.

31
00:01:19,763 --> 00:01:21,344
We have a game called Ultimate Chicken Horse,

